数十万燕郊人如何去北京上班。
How hundreds of thousands of Yanbian people go to work in Beijing.
田国宝2020-02-11 16:29。
Tian Guobao 2020-02-11 16: 29.
扫描二维码分享到朋友圈。
Scanning two-dimensional code to share with friends.
经济观察网 记者 田国宝春节假期后，与北京一河之隔的河北燕郊各个小区陆续进入封闭管理状态。
Economic observation network reporter Tian Guobao Spring Festival holiday, and Beijing across a river across the various suburban areas of Hebei into a closed management.
对小区内居民家庭出入小区进行限制出行次数、限制出行人数。
Limiting the number of trips and limiting the number of people travelling in and out of small residential areas.
甚至个别小区发出“有工作需要的居民，疫情期间请吃住在工作场所，不得返回小区”的要求。
Even individual small areas issued "work needs of the residents, during the epidemic Please eat and live in the workplace, not to return to the community."
。
.
2月10日，随着部分公司陆续开始进入复工期，小区封闭后，居民如何复工？目前各个小区要求并不相同，针对在本地工作的居民，多数小区要求，除了民生行业外，其他行业工作人员一律不得出去上班。
On February 10, as some companies began to resume work and the residential areas were closed, how did residents resume work? Currently, the requirements are not the same in each neighbourhood. For residents working in the local community, most small areas require that no worker in any industry other than the livelihood sector should go to work.
也有少数小区提供单位工作证明后，办理相关出入证明。
There are also a few small areas to provide unit work certificates after processing relevant discrepancy certificates.
。
.
此外，在燕郊生活居住、在北京工作的大约有数十万人，这些人如何到北京上班？2月11日，经济观察网记者致电燕郊某居委会，工作人员表示，目前针对北京的上班族还没有出台具体措施，。
In addition, about hundreds of thousands of people live and work in Beijing, and how do they get to work in Beijing.On Feb. 11, the Economic Watch network called a neighborhood committee in Yanbian and said there were no specific measures aimed at Beijing office workers.
“我们正在研究北京上班出行方案，可能会针对北京上班族发放专门的出入通行证，但现在还没有具体措施。
"We are looking at work travel plans in Beijing and may issue special access passes for office workers in Beijing, but there are no specific measures in place.
”上述工作人员表示，预计本周内会有相关措施出台，当前针对个别急需到北京上班的重要行业，居委会根据实际情况登记后通知物业予以放行。
The staff said measures were expected to be in place within the week and that the neighborhood committee would notify the property to let it proceed according to actual conditions in key industries where there was an urgent need to work in Beijing.
。
.
作为一个以外来人口为主的地区，1月下旬以来，随着返城人员逐步增多，燕郊在各个进出通道设立体温检测站点。
As a predominantly foreign-populated area, Yanbian temperature monitoring stations have been set up in various access roads since late January, as the number of people returning to the city has gradually increased.
同时，在官方统一要求下，辖区内小区陆续进行封闭管理，原则上要求每个小区只保留一个出入口，其他出入口全部封闭。
At the same time, under the unified official requirements, the area under the jurisdiction of the closed management, in principle, each small area to retain only one entrance, all the other access to the closed.
。
.
对于日常出行，各个小区具体要求也不一样，出行次数方面，有的小区要求每周出行3次，有的小区每天可出行1次，有的小区两天出行1次。
For daily travel, the specific requirements are also different, the number of trips, some residential areas require a weekly trip, some can travel once a day, some small areas two days trip.
但都要求每次只能1人出行，每次出行不得超过3小时。
Both require only one person to travel at a time, and each trip should not exceed three hours.
。
.
针对特殊情况，如外出就医，需要与物业公司及所在地居委会沟通，获得同意后，出行时间可超过3小时，但回到小区后，必须提供就诊证明及体温检测登记后方可进入小区。
Special circumstances, such as outside medical treatment, need to communicate with the property companies and local residents committee, after consent, travel time can exceed 3 hours, but after returning to the community, must provide a medical certificate and body temperature test registration before entering the community.
。
.
据燕郊当地一家物业公司负责防疫的工作人员透露，目前原则上要求小区内居民不得外出上班，如果的确需要上班，需要获得所在地居委会同意。
In principle, residents are not allowed to go out to work, and if they do need to work, they need the consent of their local residents, according to a staff member in charge of epidemic prevention at a local property company.
“居委会同意了，拿着公司盖章的工作证明就可以上班，居委会不同意，物业一般不敢私自放行。
"The neighborhood committee agreed, with the company seal of the work certificate can work, the neighborhood committee did not agree, the property generally do not dare to release.
”。
"
